channel.title: How to?
channel.description:
How to put a server Online so somebody else can login?
I have done these -->
[b]1. Path\Class path[/b]
[u]Classpath says:[/u] CLASSPATH=T:\Programs\Java\jdk1.6.0_17\bin;%CLASSPATH%;
[u]Path says:[/u] T:\Programs\Java\jdk1.6.0_17\bin;T:\apache-ant-1.7.1;%systemroot%\system32;%SYSTEMROOT%\System32\Wbem
[b]2. Port Forwarding [/b] (The Ip address here is my IP Address(whatismyip.com) [URL=http://img690.imageshack.us/i/27998338.png/][IMG]http://img690.imageshack.us/img690/2006/27998338.png[/img][/URL]
[b]3. No-Ip[/b]
[URL=http://img510.imageshack.us/i/16284179.png/][IMG]http://img510.imageshack.us/img510/7580/16284179.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://g.imageshack.us/img510/16284179.png/1/][IMG]http://img510.imageshack.us/img510/16284179.png/1/w708.png[/img][/URL] *
and yes I have a source, I can login the source using localhost, but I can't figure out how to let some1 else login..
What am I doing wrong? What do I need to do? If anything What IP do i give people so they can edit there settings.ini?
